---
// About.astro
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container about-inner">
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label mono muted">03 / about</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about-body">
        <p>
          I'm a CS graduate (WGU, May 2026) based in the Milwaukee area, looking for a
          junior data engineering role. My focus is on the infrastructure side of data —
          building pipelines that are reliable, documented, and maintainable rather than
          impressive to demo once.
        </p>
        <p>
          KitchenSync is my lead project: a full end-to-end forecasting system with a
          real ingestion layer, a Snowflake/dbt analytics stack, a LightGBM model, and
          a live dashboard. The other projects demonstrate pipeline automation, SQL analysis,
          and algorithm design.
        </p>
        <p>
          I currently work at Kwik Trip — which is why a kitchen production forecasting
          system was a natural problem to model.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-links">
        <a href="mailto:dakuhn1138@gmail.com" class="contact-item mono">
          <span class="accent">✉</span> dakuhn1138@gmail.com
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/dean-kuhn-565249380" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-item mono">
          <span class="accent">in</span> linkedin ↗
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/DeanKuhn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-item mono">
          <span class="accent">gh</span> github ↗
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-aside">
      <div class="aside-block">
        <div class="aside-label mono muted">education</div>
        <div class="aside-item">
          <div class="aside-title">B.S. Computer Science</div>
          <div class="aside-sub mono muted">Western Governors University · May 2026</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aside-block">
        <div class="aside-label mono muted">certifications</div>
        <div class="aside-item">
          <div class="aside-title">dbt Fundamentals</div>
          <div class="aside-sub mono muted">dbt Labs</div>
        </div>
        <div class="aside-item">
          <div class="aside-title">ITIL 4 Foundation</div>
          <div class="aside-sub mono muted">Axelos / WGU</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aside-block">
        <div class="aside-label mono muted">availability</div>
        <div class="aside-item">
          <div class="aside-title">Milwaukee area · Remote</div>
          <div class="aside-sub mono muted">Open to hybrid or on-site (greater Milwaukee)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.5;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-body p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .contact-item {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .contact-item:hover {
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* Aside */
  .about-aside {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding-top: 5.5rem; /* align with text below section header */
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-aside {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
  }

  .aside-block {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--space-md);
  }

  .aside-label {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .aside-item {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .aside-title {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .aside-sub {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
</style>
